{"id": "ChIJQVAijUJ-j4ARfJZLVQMz1Dw", "rating": 4.7, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_INEXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 4262, "displayName": {"text": "Mitchell's Ice Cream", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Family-owned ice cream shop scoops classic & creative flavors made in small batches on the premises.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJQVAijUJ-j4ARfJZLVQMz1Dw/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25welQwYzFVelkxVlVrNVdEUlFaMlEyUnpJNVduYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Great old-school ice cream parlor experience with great ice cream and innovative flavors.\n\nIf you’re looking for a new flavor combination to try, I highly suggest ordering a two-scoop sundae (hold the hot fudge) with one scoop of Mexican Chocolate and one scoop of Horchata. The pairing of chocolate, cinnamon, and that classic cookies-and-cream vibe is absolutely amazing!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Great old-school ice cream parlor experience with great ice cream and innovative flavors.\n\nIf you’re looking for a new flavor combination to try, I highly suggest ordering a two-scoop sundae (hold the hot fudge) with one scoop of Mexican Chocolate and one scoop of Horchata. The pairing of chocolate, cinnamon, and that classic cookies-and-cream vibe is absolutely amazing!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Manny", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109690735600324103601/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWylFhq81gg00NtgES8tjMNM9sixBvTkgGPUvAYCSyIOrFqRr1I=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-10T15:58:23.933276917Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25welQwYzFVelkxVlVrNVdEUlFaMlEyUnpJNVduYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25welQwYzFVelkxVlVrNVdEUlFaMlEyUnpJNVduYxAB!2m1!1s0x808f7e428d225041:0x3cd43303554b967c"}, {"name": "places/ChIJQVAijUJ-j4ARfJZLVQMz1Dw/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xKa1lVRmlhalYzZERaNFoxOVRaSFJEVVdOcFVFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "9 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Listen- this is coming from someone with a dairy intolerance and this place is great. While they do have a smaller selection for “vegan” they do a splendid job at the flavors. I couldn’t decide between vegan matcha or strawberry, sampled both, loved both, and got both! strawberry flavor tasted just as I remembered dairy strawberry to taste & matcha ice cream was delicious and creamy!\nParking was limited but had no problem finding a spot in the neighborhood. Add this to your itinerary.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Listen- this is coming from someone with a dairy intolerance and this place is great. While they do have a smaller selection for “vegan” they do a splendid job at the flavors. I couldn’t decide between vegan matcha or strawberry, sampled both, loved both, and got both! strawberry flavor tasted just as I remembered dairy strawberry to taste & matcha ice cream was delicious and creamy!\nParking was limited but had no problem finding a spot in the neighborhood. Add this to your itinerary.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Lily and Mel", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111683094979008301979/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUIks18ETiOjkQKN4tDyNoMRAS0xnB_e5Xp8A_SOchdyAJV8Vw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2025-10-09T20:47:48.649166657Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xKa1lVRmlhalYzZERaNFoxOVRaSFJEVVdOcFVFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xKa1lVRmlhalYzZERaNFoxOVRaSFJEVVdOcFVFRRAB!2m1!1s0x808f7e428d225041:0x3cd43303554b967c"}, {"name": "places/ChIJQVAijUJ-j4ARfJZLVQMz1Dw/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tscGRVWlVYMnRZUmpNMWIzQktORFJLY1RKa1VrRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I loved that they have parking in the back because that’s a huge deal in SF. Their flavors are very unique, I tried the Thai tea which was amazing as was the espresso toffee crunch. My wife really liked their chocolate caramel crunch flavor too. I was excited to try their ube but unfortunately I sampled it and tasted pretty much no ube flavor it was just purple lol. But I’d def recommend Mitchell’s for anybody that wants good ice cream in the area or wants to switch up from the usual flavors", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I loved that they have parking in the back because that’s a huge deal in SF. Their flavors are very unique, I tried the Thai tea which was amazing as was the espresso toffee crunch. My wife really liked their chocolate caramel crunch flavor too. I was excited to try their ube but unfortunately I sampled it and tasted pretty much no ube flavor it was just purple lol. But I’d def recommend Mitchell’s for anybody that wants good ice cream in the area or wants to switch up from the usual flavors", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "It’sYaBoyUzzi", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100213163442130805549/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWNs6xst576wOmsHnQ6jiuHMIQHvQl9KhhHC9HQx64KxEs96Y1h=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-13T05:41:40.112886091Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tscGRVWlVYMnRZUmpNMWIzQktORFJLY1RKa1VrRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tscGRVWlVYMnRZUmpNMWIzQktORFJLY1RKa1VrRRAB!2m1!1s0x808f7e428d225041:0x3cd43303554b967c"}, {"name": "places/ChIJQVAijUJ-j4ARfJZLVQMz1Dw/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25ORlZ6bHNaV3BsZVZKTlgzYzVabVJKYjA5MmFuYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Busy place so expect to wait. Don’t forget to grab a number ticket.\nLimited parking in the rear.\nStaff is friendly and a small place with a bench or two on the outside.\nIce cream options are plentiful.\nTaste test before committing.\nOverall, a good old school spot for old school ice cream.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Busy place so expect to wait. Don’t forget to grab a number ticket.\nLimited parking in the rear.\nStaff is friendly and a small place with a bench or two on the outside.\nIce cream options are plentiful.\nTaste test before committing.\nOverall, a good old school spot for old school ice cream.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "David Huey", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102700845748309671516/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVq6gA2Be2t8tF7Hmrq4aEqFAW78UIewc_u9mAFU_OUiDkhFZizKw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-12T19:27:42.063242916Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25ORlZ6bHNaV3BsZVZKTlgzYzVabVJKYjA5MmFuYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25ORlZ6bHNaV3BsZVZKTlgzYzVabVJKYjA5MmFuYxAB!2m1!1s0x808f7e428d225041:0x3cd43303554b967c"}, {"name": "places/ChIJQVAijUJ-j4ARfJZLVQMz1Dw/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25SNlpVMTVTVVZDVG5vellVTlZhRE0xTUZwcFNuYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Very popular ice cream spot between the Mission & Noe Valley. I lived a few blocks away for a few years and whenever I walked by here, there was pretty much always a line. This made me keen to try it.\n\nWe went on a Saturday evening and there were around 30 other people in line and hanging around. You have to take a number inside, and they'll call numbers out over a speaker when they're ready for you. There were a few servers, so the line moved reasonably quickly. We waited around 20 minutes to be served.\n\nThey have a long list of ice cream flavors, some of which are really unique. I tried the Thai tea and the peanut butter, both of which were delicious.\n\nI'd come here again on a warm evening when I had flexibility to wait a while.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Very popular ice cream spot between the Mission & Noe Valley. I lived a few blocks away for a few years and whenever I walked by here, there was pretty much always a line. This made me keen to try it.\n\nWe went on a Saturday evening and there were around 30 other people in line and hanging around. You have to take a number inside, and they'll call numbers out over a speaker when they're ready for you. There were a few servers, so the line moved reasonably quickly. We waited around 20 minutes to be served.\n\nThey have a long list of ice cream flavors, some of which are really unique. I tried the Thai tea and the peanut butter, both of which were delicious.\n\nI'd come here again on a warm evening when I had flexibility to wait a while.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Laura", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105750742486353378395/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUIKelBWTWhrkjDai6m6XL2lWYwYTotjddGAiB_wcYxLoESoqx0YQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-15T17:56:28.713512733Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25SNlpVMTVTVVZDVG5vellVTlZhRE0xTUZwcFNuYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25SNlpVMTVTVVZDVG5vellVTlZhRE0xTUZwcFNuYxAB!2m1!1s0x808f7e428d225041:0x3cd43303554b967c"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJQVAijUJ-j4ARfJZLVQMz1Dw/photos/AWCwydi1Cz